se xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jnc1665702576977.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jnc1665702576977.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jnc1665702576977.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jnc1665702576977\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jnc1665702576977___entname_261929\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__topic_d82571e1_d82572e1_d82573e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__p_d82574e1_d82575e1_d82576e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__topic_d54487e1_d54488e1_d54489e1_d54490e1_d54491e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d620074e74\">Parameters </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jnc1665702576977__table_d8420e1_d8421e1_d8422e1__entry__3\">\n Name of an entity. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__topic_d54492e1_d54493e1_d54494e1_d54495e1_d54496e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d620074e128\">Return Values </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__li_d34112e1_d34113e1_d34114e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is not present, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> returns the name of the current entity (in uppercase). If there is no current entity (that is, if the last node of the active path is not a field or entity), <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> returns an empty string (\"\").\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__li_d34115e1_d34116e1_d34117e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is present, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> returns the name of the entity if it is present in the component, otherwise <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> returns an empty string (\"\").\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__topic_d54497e1_d54498e1_d54499e1_d54500e1_d54501e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d620074e161\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__topic_d54502e1_d54503e1_d54504e1_d54505e1_d54506e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d620074e171\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__p_d82592e1_d82593e1_d82594e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> function is useful when you are writing global ProcScript, because it allows you to generalize your code. It is also useful to examine this function when you are using the ProcScript debugger to step through ProcScript statements.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__section_rb5_hjy_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d620074e183\">Example: Inserting a New Occurrence</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows a call to a global ProcScript in the\n               entity's create trigger to insert a new occurrence before the first occurrence or to\n               add a new occurrence after the last occurrence:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__pre_sk2_3jy_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger create\n call AddInsertOcc()\n if ($rettype = 65)\n creocc $entname, -1\n else\n creocc $entname, 1\n endif\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__section_yl1_gjy_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d620074e198\">Example: Testing a Condition</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span> returns the current entity name, and that\n               may not always be the entity you expect. For example, if ENTITY1 occurs before ENTITY\n               2 in the component structure, retrieving data for ENTITY2 does not make it the\n               current entity. You can ensure that you are dealing with the correct entity by using\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">setocc</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jnc1665702576977__pre_hml_gjy_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">retrieve ENTITY2\nif ($entname = \"ENTITY1\")\n setocc \"ENTITY2\"\nendif\n...\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yga1665702577055.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$applname</a><p>Return the name of the Application Shell.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exa1665702598712.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curocc</a><p>Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jfn1665702577202.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldname</a><p>Return the name of the current field or check for the presence of a specified field in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ksm1665702577277.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancename</a><p>Return the name of the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ehv1665702690624.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$rettype</a><p>Return the retrieval mode of the outermost entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$entname Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component. $entname { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Name of an entity. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values If Entity is not present, $entname returns the name of the current entity (in uppercase). If there is no current entity (that is, if the last node of the active path is not a field or entity), $entname returns an empty string (\"\"). If Entity is present, $entname returns the name of the entity if it is present in the component, otherwise $entname returns an empty string (\"\"). Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $entname function is useful when you are writing global ProcScript, because it allows you to generalize your code. It is also useful to examine this function when you are using the ProcScript debugger to step through ProcScript statements. Example: Inserting a New Occurrence The following example shows a call to a global ProcScript in the entity's create trigger to insert a new occurrence before the first occurrence or to add a new occurrence after the last occurrence: trigger create call AddInsertOcc() if ($rettype = 65) creocc $entname, -1 else creocc $entname, 1 endif end Copy Example: Testing a Condition $entname returns the current entity name, and that may not always be the entity you expect. For example, if ENTITY1 occurs before ENTITY 2 in the component structure, retrieving data for ENTITY2 does not make it the current entity. You can ensure that you are dealing with the correct entity by using setocc . retrieve ENTITY2 if ($entname = \"ENTITY1\") setocc \"ENTITY2\" endif ... Copy Related Links $applname Return the name of the Application Shell. $curocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist. $fieldname Return the name of the current field or check for the presence of a specified field in the component. $instancename Return the name of the current component instance. $rettype Return the retrieval mode of the outermost entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}